Mechanics In this precision 3D platformer you will fall a lot, but its important to remember that you just need to jump up. Every jump is a carefully through out Mega Jump which needs to be planned out according to the height and length needed for the Mega Jump. The longer you charge your jump, the higher you go but you also go shorter . Same for the opposite, charge for less and you go further but lower . Will you Megajump to the top? or will you mega jump and fail. Megafall
